{"title":"狂欢","authors":["田","间"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂 欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田 间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元宵节，在浙江东阳县观李宅、许宅公社等盛大灯会和参加樟村公社群众诗会志兴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛大的节日！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众的狂欢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙腾虎跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争芳斗妍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看吧，四方灯火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着东阳笑颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤红的灯海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的大川；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限光热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃在胸间！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试看多少火柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞得地转天翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光之奔流呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春之花枝呀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天响炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动地管弦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我张开双臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高呼人民万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨塔在火中悬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨树在灯中飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民之心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何以比美？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵有天才歌手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能把它描绘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉祥的歌鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕着东阳转；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粒粒火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵春雷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起能工巧匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同造山乡新宫殿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，花灯千奇百巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，金龙千串万串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界少有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里去看？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝愿大众歌手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作四化雷电！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛大的节日！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众的狂欢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春开红枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁回绿野；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就是光、火焰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就是世上仙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上哪有此春色？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"返老还童把我牵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上哪有此春色？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫千红金不换！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢东阳情万担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠我歌海和灯山！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}